casebody.data:
STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Amanda Caye DREIER, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-1403 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 17, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Amanda Dreier appeals from the sentence imposed upon her plea of guilty to conspiracy to commit a felony, sexual exploitation by a school employee. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
